  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">PIEDAR will implement a Project called &quot;Centre for Environmental Education through Participatory Action Learning&quot; (CEEPAL). A national network of schools is imparting environmental education through participatory action learning. The project also demonstrates values and shares knowledge for sustainable development in Pakistan and seeks to influence Government policies and practices for Environmental Education. Special attention is given to communicating climate change.</narrative>
